# Each subdirectory under workspaces/ is a per-environment NocoBase project
# (DSL + state.yaml). These are local deployment data, not tool source — keep
# them out of the shared repo so individual users / branches / NB instances
# don't conflict with each other.
#
# To track a specific project intentionally (e.g., a shared sample), add an
# explicit allow-list line below.
*
!.gitignore
!README.md
